[[!meta title="Tale of the Thunderbolt"]]
[[!tag books books/scifi]]

Back to the Vampire Earth series by E. E. Knight. After an mildly
interesting start, the book turns decidedly soporific, It is a
travelogue for a Caribbean trip that Valentine takes, with a few
mildly intriguing variations. I think that a non-loner role for
Valentine does not work.
